org.batfish.datamodel

Class AclIpSpace

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.datamodel.IpSpace
      • org.batfish.datamodel.AclIpSpace
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<IpSpace>

    public class AclIpSpace
extends IpSpace
    An ACL-based IpSpace. An IP is permitted if it is in the space the ACL represents, or denied if it is not.
